sub_title: Communication and Content Creation in German - English - Dutch, Marketing Communications / Event Manager, Customer Service
summary:
Senior marketing and communications professional. Multilingual German, Dutch, English.

Specialties: Fluent communication in three languages. Customer and partner relations. 
Brand positioning, content creation, event / online marketing, promotions, press relations.

Industries: Internet SaaS (Nedstat/ Comscore), Entertainment / Tourism (Walt Disney Company), Advertising (Leo Burnett), Floral industry (EFSA European association of floral and lifestyle sector), Publishing (Editor Lifestyle magazine)

Languages: German, English, Dutch

Board Member Foundation OOPOEH / www.oopeoh.nl

Volunteer (Communications) at Stichting Stolpersteine www.stichting-stolpersteine.nl

Own website: www.dogsenjoyamsterdam.com
